Title: Look Out, Here They Come!
Plot: Jenny's boss's daughter is getting married and Shane gets a gig as the hair stylist at her wedding. Kit and Max spot a young girl who's obsessed with Jenny's work and hook her up with her dream job. Alice and Tasha go on a double-date with Bette and Jodi. Meanwhile in prison, Helena is rescued by her cell mate.
GuestStars: Lynda Boyd, Barbara Kottmeier, Michelle Morgan, Alberta Mayne, Alexis Kellum Creer, Anthony McRae, Lenore Zann, Pamela Diaz, Charlie Carrick
